The compatible android version for this project is Android 4.4 or above.

1. Press "Capture" button to enter camera preview mode.
2. Put 1 resistor in front of a white background.
3. Zoom in and make sure the resistor is horizontal. The resistor should be as large as possible and tolerance band(gold or silver color band) should be on the right hand side.
4. After the image is captured, press white circle below the image view to process. It took 2 or 3 seconds to show the result.
5. Press "Capture" button will allow user to reenter camera access mode(back to step 1).

